text=(:title Pinkerton Station:)%0ahttp://wantonwicked.gamingsandbox.com/wiki/images/werewolftheforsaken.png%0a%0aReturn to: [[CityBook.?|Venue Locations]], [[CityBook.HistoricalDistrict|District Locations]], [[CityBook.CityBook|The City]]%0a%0a[[#location]]%0a!!The Pinkerton Station%0a'''District:''' Historic District%0a%0a%25width=730%25http://i.imgur.com/5HTMT2w.jpg %0a%0aKitchen open 24/7 %0a%0aNo alcohol 3 AM to 7AM Monday through Saturday.%0aNo Alcohol 2:55 AM Sunday til 7 AM Monday%0a%0aBadges, guns, and police man blue dominate the bar. The police of Savannah tend to congregate at this bar after their shifts. People with warrents or gang colors quickly find themselves interrogated or arrested if they wander into the bar.%0a%0aIronically enough a number of small crimes happen daily in The Pinkerton Station perpetuated by the police. Police officers will usually be playing cards and gambling at a table. Underage servers, always of direct relation to police officers, will stay clocked in once the liquor starts flowing and keep serving patrons. Children can often be spotted on a bar stool being supervised by the bartender as they wait for their police parents to get off shift.%0a%0a%0a'''Resonance:''' Silent Loyalty\\%0a'''Territory:''' Falls within Whispering Pines Hegemony claim%0a[[#locationend]]%0a%0a----%0a(:include CityBook.Directory:)
