cters are using it.%0a632,636c695,699%0a%3c *'''Thunderbolt''' (ooooo)\\%0a%3c Cost: 2 Essence\\%0a%3c Dice Pool: Manipulation+Survival+Honor - Stamina\\%0a%3c Action: Instant\\%0a%3c Success: The bolt deals two lethal damage per success. Magical armor sources (Rage Armor, Mage Armor, etc.) are added to the target's stamina when defending. As the damage is lighting based, creatures immune to electricity are unaffected (or, in Promethean's case, healed).\\%0a---%0a> *'''Thunderbolt''' (ooooo)%0a> Cost: 2 Essence%0a> Dice Pool: Manipulation+Survival+Honor - Stamina%0a> Action: Instant%0a> Success: The bolt deals two lethal damage per success. Magical armor sources (Rage Armor, Mage Armor, etc.) are added to the target's stamina when defending. As the damage is lighting based, creatures immune to electricity are unaffected (or, in Promethean's case, healed).%0a638c701,702%0a%3c [[#HRGE | Back to Gift Errata]]\\%0a---%0a> [[#HRGE | Back to Gift Errata]]%0a> \\%0a
